name: Supervisor Wise Production  Casting Treatment
query:
select a.supervisor,a.supervisor_name,a.treatment_date,a.treatment_time,a.shift,a.shift_time,a.casting_treatment,
b.item_code,b.item_name,b.pouring,b.available_quantity,b.processed_quantity,b.quantity,b.casting_weight
from `tabCasting Treatment` a
left join `tabCasting Treatment Casting Item` b on a.name = b.parent
